        "title": "肉末茄子煲！配这菜我能吃3碗饭",
        "content": "<p>茄子算是大家餐桌上常出现的蔬菜吧，茄子好吃是好吃，但是最大的一个问题就是太费油，还不容易炒软。油放太多吧不健康，不放吧不好吃。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-178a2778310c50dd?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>有没有一种做法是既少油又软绵入味？当然有，在烤箱里烤一下会变软，不过没烤箱的怎么办。别急，今天就来说一个更方便好吃的做法。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-8812263dcf7efc43?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>快来看看怎么做~</p><p>茄子肉末煲</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-85c294b164b15c22?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>食材：</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-75c7d73369facdc6?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>茄子、肉末、大蒜、豆瓣酱、料酒、生抽</p><p>做法：</p><p>1、将茄子洗净切条，撒盐腌制10分钟使其出水。咱们的小聪明就在此，用盐腌制后把水分逼出来，茄子会变软少吸油。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-128724eb003c8320?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>2、将猪肉洗净切末，放入半勺盐、一勺料酒、两勺生抽腌制15-20分钟。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-dbccbd3aa83de459?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>3、热锅放一点点油，放入大蒜爆香，放入肉末炒至变色，加入一勺料酒、两勺豆瓣酱翻炒均匀。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-9822eabce793f21f?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>4、将腌制好的茄子挤干水分，放入锅中与肉末翻炒均匀。过油的目的是使茄子不变色。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-ca64473f9a20c8ae?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>5、将茄子肉末放入砂锅中，放入半碗水中火煮8分钟左右，最后撒上葱花就可以啦。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-1f0e99026d2711fe?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><p>6、这样做出来的茄子，色香味俱全，保持着茄子的紫色，茄香浓郁，味道绵软入味。关键是少油，健康又营养。</p><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-5fda49e8461dd351?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-c267b22954be3db2?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/><img src='//upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12095765-67fff8a95bd607c5?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/720/format/webp' alt=''/>"
    }
}